  "_doc": "Scan universe. The full Option Panda / Finviz list (avg vol > 400K, price > $1) drives the analysis; the scanner cheaply prefilters it down to prefilter.max_chain_scan names before the expensive option-chain scan. breadth_sample feeds the regime breadth component.",
